Write a Python program to perform statistical analysis on marks obtained in FDS (Fundamentals of Data Structures).
The program should:

1. Accept marks of n students (enter 0 for absent students).

2. Display a menu to perform the following operations:

      Calculate the average marks of the class.

      Find the highest and lowest marks.

      Count the number of students absent for the test.

      Display the marks with the highest frequency.

      Exit the program.
